name: v0.1.0
body:
## Summary

* Support import feed URL from OPML file
* Implement cache saving and loading (Improved performance)
* Fix bugs

## What's Changed

* Fix/exitcode by @sheepla in https://github.com/sheepla/srss/pull/18
* support import feed URL from OPML file by @hashue in https://github.com/sheepla/srss/pull/16
* ensure `.test` directory exists by @elderica in https://github.com/sheepla/srss/pull/26
* use empty slice when we cannot read URL entries by @elderica in https://github.com/sheepla/srss/pull/25
* Implement renderHTML() #13 by @sheepla in https://github.com/sheepla/srss/pull/29
* Implement cache saving and loading (`encoding/gob` format) by @sheepla in https://github.com/sheepla/srss/pull/31

## New Contributors

* @elderica made their first contribution in https://github.com/sheepla/srss/pull/26

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/sheepla/srss/compare/v0.0.2...v0.1.0
